		<h2>Can I contribute to the project?</h2>
		<p>
			Yes, please do! :D if you understand web design or have experience reverse engineering programs on Mac/Linux, or if you think that you can be helpful in some other way, shoot us an email at <code>support@isaactracker.com</code>
		</p>
		<p>We'll make sure to get back to you ASAP.</p>
